snippet.title: CHALLENGE: If YOU LAUGH you need to RESTART THE COMPILATION! So can you finish it? - Funny KIDS
snippet.description:
These kid fails are so hilarious! Here are the rules of the challenge: watch the video and every time that you laugh you need to start watching the compilation from the beginning again! So can you finish the whole video? Hope you like our compilation, please share it and SUBSCRIBE! Watch also our other videos!
